Updates
~~~~~~~

    I may continue with this, depending on the response.  If you send
 me $3 US dollars (yes three!) I will EMail you 3 megs of updates,
 staggered in half meg or so chunks (I only have 1 meg of space on my
 host server, maybe you only have that much too!).  Otherwise you'll
 just have to download it yourself.  All this may change, depending
 on the response.


